Home Page :

1. There will be a stack of real time, latest questions asked on the site, we'll also provide link to popular questions, having more views, more discussions.
2. Users can also post articles. Latest articles will be on top, we'll provide a link to search featured/popular articles.
2. There will a separate search box where users can search answers and articles within website, the search can be customized by adding filters using tags of technologies.
3. A person who asks question will provide tags to the question based upon the technology(programming language, platform) he/she asking question about.
4. A link to users profile.
5. Follow other users.
6. About us, contact us, feedback, complaints,
7. Debugger poll : a simple question like a survey will accept an answer from multiple choices.
